Maintainer: Sevvandi Kandanaarachchi <sevvandik@gmail.com>
Description: A set of statistical tools for spatio-temporal data exploration. 
    Includes simple plotting functions, covariance computations and 
    computations similar to PCA. Can use both dataframes and stars objects for
    all plots and computations.
